  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个时序数据可视化系统的ER模型，核心是一个叫Timescape Viewer的模块，它要管理多个数据源和可视化窗口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape",
        "Origin",
        "Window"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Timescape作为中心实体。那它和Origin之间是什么关系？一个Timescape可以对接多个数据源吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape",
        "Origin"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，一对多的关系，用origins来命名这条关系线。Origin记录name字段，标识数据来源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Timescape",
        "Origin",
        "origins"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Timescape和Origin的一对多关系已建立。接下来Window实体需要定义时间范围，我加上begin和end两个Timestamp字段，还有一个live模式标记。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "begin",
        "end",
        "live"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Window也要和Timescape关联，同样是Timescape可以管理多个Window。另外我们需要ScopeLegend和ScopePlotter两个组件来处理图例和绘图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter",
        "Timescape",
        "Window"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ScopeLegend和ScopePlotter都是Timescape直接管理的吗？它们需要字段吗，还是作为空壳配置实体？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScopeLegend",
        "ScopePlotter",
        "Timescape"
